text: Stefanie Scott (born December 6, 1996) is an American actress and singer. She is best known for her role as Lexi Reed in the television series, A.N.T. Farm. She has been in TV shows and movies on the Disney Channel. She had a role in the movie No Strings Attached. She has won two Young Artist Awards and a Behind the Voice Actors Award. == References == Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:American child actors Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Chicago
